## ğŸ”§ `deployment.yaml` (Helm template)

```yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: {{ include "user-service.fullname" . }}
  labels:
    app: {{ include "user-service.name" . }}
spec:
  replicas: {{ .Values.replicaCount }}
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: {{ include "user-service.name" . }}
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: {{ include "user-service.name" . }}
    spec:
      containers:
        - name: {{ .Chart.Name }}
          image: "{{ .Values.image.repository }}:{{ .Values.image.tag }}"
          ports:
            - containerPort: 8080
          env:
            - name: SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE
              value: {{ .Values.spring.profile }}
            - name: DB_PASSWORD
              valueFrom:
                secretKeyRef:
                  name: db-secret
                  key: db-password
```

---

## ğŸ”§ `service.yaml`

```yaml
apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: {{ include "user-service.fullname" . }}
spec:
  type: ClusterIP
  ports:
    - port: 80
      targetPort: 8080
  selector:
    app: {{ include "user-service.name" . }}
```

---

## ğŸ”§ `ingress.yaml`

```yaml
apiVersion: networking.k8s.io/v1
kind: Ingress
metadata:
  name: {{ include "user-service.fullname" . }}
  annotations:
    kubernetes.io/ingress.class: nginx
spec:
  rules:
    - host: {{ .Values.ingress.host }}
      http:
        paths:
          - path: /
            pathType: Prefix
            backend:
              service:
                name: {{ include "user-service.fullname" . }}
                port:
                  number: 80
```

